assay_description: Inhibition of Norovirus 3CLpro using Edans-DFHLQ/GP-Dabcyl as substrate preincubated for 30 mins followed by substrate addition measured after 1 hr by FRET assay
Antiviral activity against Norovirus replicon infected in human HG23 cells assessed as inhibition of viral RNA replication after 48 hrs by qRT-PCR method
